<m0>Police spread too<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 2.01 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>thin, residents say<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS 1.30 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
